English Up Privacy Policy
Last Updated: January 2025

1. Data Collection
English Up does not collect any personal information from users. All data stored locally on your device.

2. In-App Purchases
Our app uses Apple's in-app purchase system for premium/pro features, managed through RevenueCat. All payment processing is handled directly by Apple, and subscription management is handled by RevenueCat. Neither we nor RevenueCat have access to your payment information. For more information about RevenueCat's privacy policy, you can visit https://www.revenuecat.com/privacy/

3. Children's Privacy
Our services are not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.

4. Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Users will be notified of any changes through app updates.
    

5. Contact
If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us at: mangaboya233@gmail.com
